N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 10400.6 - Confidentiality of Records

State Regulations

The confidentiality of the commission's records shall be
governed by section 499-g of the Judiciary Law. Disciplining staff for breaches
of confidentiality shall be governed by procedures set forth in section 499-h
of the Judiciary Law. Notes
